verbose_text: Two-way ANOVA showed a main effect of treatment (F = 38.59, df 1,16 p < 0.0001) and an interaction of treatment and genotype (F 1,16 = 6.05, p = 0.026) and Bonferroni post hoc comparison showed that ME7 + LPS was significantly more affected than ME7 IL-1R1 -/- + LPS (p < 0.05) and ME7 + saline (p < 0.001), although LPS still increased apoptosis somewhat in IL-1RI -/- (p < 0.05).
evidence: LPS still increased apoptosis somewhat in IL-1RI -/-
